## Create a new author (admin only)

POST {{baseUrl}}/author
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "bio": "Experienced tech writer and AI researcher",
  "profile_image": "https://example.com/profile.jpg",
  "website": "https://janedoe.com",
  "social_media": {
    "twitter": "https://twitter.com/janedoe",
    "linkedin": "https://linkedin.com/in/janedoe"
  }
}

###

## Get all authors

GET {{baseUrl}}/author

###

## Get popular authors

GET {{baseUrl}}/author/popular

###

## Get author by ID

GET {{baseUrl}}/author/4

###

## Get author by slug

GET {{baseUrl}}/author/slug/test2-user2

###

## Update an author (full update) (admin only)

PUT {{baseUrl}}/author/4
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

{
  "name": "Test2 User2",
  "bio": "Experienced tech writer and AI researcher",
  "profile_image": "https://example.com/profile-updated.jpg",
  "website": "https://test2user2.com",
  "social_media": {
    "twitter": "https://twitter.com/test2user2",
    "linkedin": "https://linkedin.com/in/johndoe",
    "github": "https://github.com/johndoe"
  }
}

###

## Partially update an author (admin only)

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/author/4
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

{
  "bio": "Updated biography with new information"
}

###

## Add or update social media link (admin only)

POST {{baseUrl}}/author/4/social-media
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

{
  "platform": "youtube",
  "url": "https://youtube.com/c/johnsmith"
}

###

## Delete social media link (admin only)

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/author/4/social-media/github
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

###

## Delete an author (admin only)

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/author/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

